name: Mad Bull Token
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en:
This is giveaway-centered, meme-based, reflective crypto token launched on the Binance Smart Chain.

This meme is based off The BULL MARKET wich the most common term on trading, MAD does the suggestion of agressive and huge profits.

It has genuine use-case and will be community-centered directly giving back to our investors and aiming to make our own decentralised platform to be the biggest out there, with massive marketing.
